title: Spider-Men 01-05 (2012, Digital, Zone-Empire)
description: This terrific miniseries shows what happens when Peter Parker from the regular Marvel Universe meets Miles Morales for the Ultimate Universe! It's a great team-up and a fun story that highlights both mens' strengths and differences. Especially poignant given Slott's Superior Spider-Man is soon to end and Parker will be back as Spider-Man soon! Brian Michael Bendis, who more or less created the Ultimate Spider-Man from the ground up, writes this nice little one-off tale. This digital copy is thanks to Zone-Empire, much appreciated as always. Please seed, and enjoy! :-)
